            "id": 127087,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Ensuite vient le nom de la fonction en camel case, comme <code>greetUser</code>, suivi de parenthèses, <code>(</code> et <code>)</code>.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"5\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"15\" /><option startIndex=\"15\" endIndex=\"16\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>greetUser</code> suivi de <code>(</code> et enfin <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Braces",
            "id": 127088,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Les accolades <code>{</code> et <code>}</code> délimitent le bloc de code qui appartient à la fonction.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"17\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"22\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>{</code> suivi de <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Between braces",
            "id": 127089,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Le code que nous voulons regrouper se place entre les accolades. Cette fonction regroupe deux instructions <code>print()</code> liées.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"func\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greetUser\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Good morning Anna&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome back&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"48\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"53\" endIndex=\"69\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>print</code> suivi de <code>(\"Welcome back\")</code>.</p></body></html>"
